---
import LegalLayout from '../../layouts/LegalLayout.astro';
import { SITE, CONTACT } from '../../lib/site';

const lang = 'en' as const;
---

<LegalLayout
  lang={lang}
  pageKey="cookies"
  title="Cookie policy | Alma Mía"
  description="Cookie policy of Alma Mía: which cookies the site uses, for what purpose and how to manage them, pursuant to the Spanish LSSI-CE and data protection regulations."
  h1="Cookie policy"
  lastUpdated="14/06/2026"
>
  <p>
    This policy explains what cookies are and which ones the website {SITE.domain} uses, in
    accordance with the Spanish LSSI-CE and the guidelines of the Spanish Data Protection Agency.
  </p>

  <h2>1. What are cookies?</h2>
  <p>
    Cookies are small files that are downloaded to your device when you visit certain websites
    and that allow, among other things, preferences to be remembered or the use of the site to
    be measured.
  </p>

  <h2>2. Cookies used by this site</h2>
  <p>
    This site currently uses only Vercel analytics (Vercel Web Analytics and Speed Insights), a
    solution that <strong>does not use cookies</strong> nor collect identifiable personal data,
    and therefore does not require prior consent.
  </p>
  <p>
    Should measurement or advertising tools that do use cookies be incorporated in the future
    (for example, Google Analytics 4, Google Tag Manager or advertising pixels), this policy will
    be updated and a consent banner compliant with Consent Mode v2 will be enabled, so that such
    cookies are only activated after your acceptance.
  </p>

  <h2>3. Managing cookies</h2>
  <p>
    You can allow, block or delete the cookies installed on your device from your browser's
    settings. Consult your browser's help to find out how to do so.
  </p>

  <h2>4. More information</h2>
  <p>
    If you have any questions about this cookie policy, you can write to us at {CONTACT.email}.
  </p>
</LegalLayout>
